			)
			(table_cell "1. Add a manual reset function. Press and hold the button and place the device on the charger to reset the MCU.\n2. Change the power input rectifier bridge circuit to an anti-reverse connection circuit to reduce the voltage drop caused by the input diode and avoid affecting the charging current.\n3. Add power control of the RF analog switch to save power consumption."
				(exclude_from_sim no)
				(at 68.58 93.98 0)
				(size 113.03 27.94)
