			(table_cell "1. Updated the layout to solve the problem of poor WiFi 2.4G signal\n2. Changed the vibration motor to LDO power supply to improve vibration reliability\n3. Changed the positioning pin of J1 to NC, which is short-circuited with the signal pin on the connector"
				(exclude_from_sim no)
